{
  "texts": [
    "Finally, we take the 16 edited responses and choose one with the highest reward as scored by Llama-3.1-Nemotron-70B-Reward.",
    "As shown in Fig. 2, scaling from 2 to 16 initial responses per prompt leads to an increase in Arena Hard from 89.0 (95% CI: -1.4, 1.2) to 90.2 (95% CI: -1.6, 1.2).",
    "This suggests that the Feedback-Edit setup is complementary to Best-of-N sampling.",
    "Effective Feedback per Response Our baseline setup in Sec.",
    "3.1 generates 10 feedback per response."
  ]
}